{"tid":2375076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荷蘭周末實施宵禁防止變種新型冠狀病毒傳播","createTime":"2021-01-21T17:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T18:01:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea218f9adfbfd9d80c26ed83e18c1fd2964fe0e5","tid":2375076,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571691-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571691-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TSfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=1519d2fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571691-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed22a405\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571691-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭將於當地星期六起實施宵禁，是二戰以來首次，以防止變種的新型冠狀病毒傳播，預料至少實施至2月。<br />\n<br />\n宵禁在每晚九時至翌日凌晨4時半實施，較首相呂特原本建議的開始時間遲半小時，這個方案獲大部分國會議員支持。民眾只能在有迫切需要的情況下，在宵禁時段外出，包括緊急醫療需要和必要工作等。違反宵禁令的人士會被罰款95歐元。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭的疫情過去3星期有緩和趨勢，但當地衛生部門憂慮，若不收緊社交距離措施，變種病毒將在下月引來新一波反彈。"},{"pid":"4d48f0e08b1eb27caf1ab45198102b6b3421ca3a","tid":2375076,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係「變種中国武漢肺炎病毒」"}]}